# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# NOTE: src/pages/index.astro already serves a localStorage-aware client-side
# redirect (with <meta http-equiv="refresh"> as the JS-disabled fallback).
# We don't add a server-side `/ → /ru/` 302 here, because that would override
# the client logic and break the saved-language preference.
#
# Trailing-slash hygiene: send the no-trailing-slash forms to canonical URLs.
/ru        /ru/        301
/tg        /tg/        301
/ru/apply  /ru/apply/  301
/tg/apply  /tg/apply/  301
/ru/about  /ru/about/  301
/tg/about  /tg/about/  301
/ru/search /ru/search/ 301
/tg/search /tg/search/ 301
